ðŸš€ 3. How to Run the Program
 Using Git
Compile all the files using:
javac managementSystem/*.java
Run the program:
java managementSystem.LibraryManage

Use the menu to:
Add books: Enter the ID, Title, Author, Genre, and Availability status.
View all books: Display all books in the catalog.
Search books: By ID or Title.
Update book details.
Delete a book.
Exit the system.

Using Jar File
To run the program using the JAR file:
java -jar DigitalLibraryManagement.jar
